<body>
	<div class="container mt-5">
		<h1 class="text-center text-warning mb-4">
			About <span style="color: white;">SwiftBite</span>
		</h1>

		<div class="card p-4">
			<p>
				Welcome to <span style="color: gold;">SwiftBite</span>, your
				one-stop destination for delicious food delivered right to your
				doorstep. Whether you’re craving a quick snack or planning a family
				meal, SwiftBite connects you with the best hotels and restaurants in
				town.
			</p>
			<p>
				As a <strong>Customer</strong>, you can:
			<ul>
				<li>Browse a wide variety of hotels and food items, complete
					with images, descriptions, and ratings.</li>
				<li>Use smart filters and a search bar to quickly find your
					favorite dish or hotel based on name, rating, or cuisine.</li>
				<li>Add items to your cart, review your selection, and place
					orders with ease.</li>
				<li>View your past orders and track current ones, ensuring
					you’re always in control.</li>
				<li>Rate and review dishes to help others discover the best
					flavors.</li>
			</ul>
			</p>
			<p>
				As a <strong>Manager</strong>, you can:
			<ul>
				<li>Register and create your own hotel profile with details and
					images.</li>
				<li>Add, edit, or remove food items from your menu, and upload
					appealing food images.</li>
				<li>Monitor incoming orders and view real-time notifications
					about customer requests.</li>
				<li>Check out detailed reports and ratings to understand
					customer preferences and grow your business.</li>
				<li>Manage hotel availability and respond quickly to customer
					needs.</li>
			</ul>
			</p>
			<p>At SwiftBite, we aim to make food ordering fast, easy, and
				enjoyable — both for customers and managers. Start your journey with
				us today!</p>
		</div>
	</div>
</body>
